COMPLETE DAX QUERIES FOR ALL TOP QUESTION PATTERNS


1. What are the active Housing/Commercial facilities in X City/Country/Area/Region?

By Country (Commercial):
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Main usage type]),'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active",'CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing]="Commercial",'CurMonData'[Country Name]="Australia")

By Country (Housing):
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Main usage type]),'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active",'CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing]="Housing",'CurMonData'[Country Name]="Australia")

By City:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[Country Name],'CurMonData'[Main usage type]),'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active",'CurMonData'[City]="Comodoro Rivadavia")

By Region:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Country Name]),'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active",'CurMonData'[Region]="Asia Pacific")

By Area (RE Region):
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Country Name]),'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active",'CurMonData'[RE Region]="Australasia")

By Hemisphere:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Country Name],'CurMonData'[Region]),'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active",'CurMonData'[Hemisphere]="Eastern")


2. What is the Net Book Value of X Facility/Country/Area/Region?

By City:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonNBV'[Arch.Obj. ID],'CurMonNBV'[Name of Architectural Object],'CurMonNBV'[City],'CurMonNBV'[Street],"NBV",SUM('CurMonNBV'[Current Year NBV]),"Next Year",SUM('CurMonNBV'[Next Year NBV]),"Total Assets",SUM('CurMonNBV'[Total Assets])),'CurMonNBV'[City]="Ciudad del Carmen")

By Facility Name:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonNBV'[Arch.Obj. ID],'CurMonNBV'[Name of Architectural Object],'CurMonNBV'[City],"NBV",SUM('CurMonNBV'[Current Year NBV])),'CurMonNBV'[Name of Architectural Object]="Comodoro Bunker")

All NBV grouped by City:
EVALUATE TOPN(20,SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonNBV'[City],"NBV",SUM('CurMonNBV'[Current Year NBV])),[NBV],DESC)

Total NBV:
EVALUATE ROW("NBV",CALCULATE([Value_NBV]))

NBV Projection:
EVALUATE ROW("NBV CY",CALCULATE([NBV_CY]),"NBV NY",CALCULATE([NBV_NY]),"NBV N2Y",CALCULATE([NBV_N2Y]),"NBV N3Y",CALCULATE([NBV_N3Y]),"NBV N4Y",CALCULATE([NBV_N4Y]),"Total",CALCULATE([NBV_TotalAsset]))


