4. What is the ROU value of X Facility/Country/Area/Region?

Total:
EVALUATE ROW("ROU",CALCULATE([Value_ROU]))

By Region:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(ROW("ROU",SUM('CurMonData'[Current Year ROU])),'CurMonData'[Region]="Asia Pacific")

By Country:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(ROW("ROU",SUM('CurMonData'[Current Year ROU])),'CurMonData'[Country Name]="Australia")

By City:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(ROW("ROU",SUM('CurMonData'[Current Year ROU])),'CurMonData'[City]="Comodoro Rivadavia")

By RE Region (Area):
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(ROW("ROU",SUM('CurMonData'[Current Year ROU])),'CurMonData'[RE Region]="Australasia")

ROU Projection:
EVALUATE ROW("ROU CY",CALCULATE(SUM('CurMonData'[Current Year ROU])),"ROU NY",CALCULATE(SUM('CurMonData'[Next year ROU])),"ROU N2Y",CALCULATE(SUM('CurMonData'[Next 2 years ROU])),"ROU N3Y",CALCULATE(SUM('CurMonData'[Next 3 years ROU])),"ROU N4Y",CALCULATE(SUM('CurMonData'[Next 4 years ROU])))

