6. What facilities do Cementing/Wireline/HCT/etc. occupy?

By PSL:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Billing File'[Region],'Billing File'[Country],'Billing File'[Facility Name],"Cost",SUM('Billing File'[Allocated USD])),'Billing File'[PSL Name]="Cementing")

By Sub PSL:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Billing File'[Region],'Billing File'[Country],'Billing File'[Facility Name],"Cost",SUM('Billing File'[Allocated USD])),'Billing File'[Sub PSL Name]="Cementing Land Services")

PSL in specific country:
