7. Provide a list of Warehouse/Plant/Manufacturing/etc. facilities globally or in X

Globally by type:
EVALUATE FILTER(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Country Name],'CurMonData'[Region]),CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[Site and Name],"Warehouse"))

By type in country:
EVALUATE FILTER(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Country Name],'CurMonData'[Region]),CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[Site and Name],"Warehouse") && 'CurMonData'[Country Name]="Australia")

By type in region:
EVALUATE FILTER(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Country Name]),CONTAINSSTRING('CurMonData'[Site and Name],"Plant") && 'CurMonData'[Region]="Latin America")

By Main usage type:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Country Name],'CurMonData'[Region]),'CurMonData'[Main usage type]="Office")

Replace: "Warehouse", "Plant", "Manufacturing", "Field Camp", "Bunker", "Office", "Mud Plant", "Land", "Storage" with whatever type user asks about.


8. What is operating expense for X period of time for Facility/Country/Area/Region?

By Country:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Billing File'[Facility Name],'Billing File'[PSL Name],"Cost",SUM('Billing File'[Allocated USD]),"FT2",SUM('Billing File'[Billable FT2])),'Billing File'[Country]="Australia")

By Region and Country:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Billing File'[Facility Name],'Billing File'[PSL Name],"Cost",SUM('Billing File'[Allocated USD]),"FT2",SUM('Billing File'[Billable FT2])),'Billing File'[Region]="Asia Pacific",'Billing File'[Country]="Australia")

By Region:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Billing File'[Country],'Billing File'[Facility Name],"Cost",SUM('Billing File'[Allocated USD])),'Billing File'[Region]="Asia Pacific")

By Facility:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Billing File'[PSL Name],"Cost",SUM('Billing File'[Allocated USD]),"FT2",SUM('Billing File'[Billable FT2]),"Pct",SUM('Billing File'[% of Site Cost])),'Billing File'[Facility Name]="Brisbane Office Level 11")

