12. Provide a list of active housing/commercial facilities in X for a specific time period

By Commercial/Housing with Term End filter:
EVALUATE CALCULATETABLE(SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('CurMonData'[Site and Name],'CurMonData'[City],'CurMonData'[Country Name],'CurMonData'[Term End],'CurMonData'[Main usage type]),'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated]="Active",'CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing]="Commercial",'CurMonData'[Country Name]="Australia")

Note: Time period filtering uses the Term End column. The model shows current snapshot data not historical. For past periods, data may not be available. Inform user: "The model shows current active data. I can filter by contract term end dates but cannot show historical state at a past date."


