CRITICAL DAX RULES:
1. SUM('CurMonData'[column]) for ALL CurMonData aggregation columns
2. CALCULATE([measure]) for KeyMeasures measures only
3. Billing File uses [Country]. CurMonData uses [Country Name]. NEVER mix them.
4. Filter values are case-sensitive
5. Table names with spaces need quotes: 'Billing File', 'Need Attention'
6. Replace filter values with whatever user asks about
7. Never show DAX to users
